        "title": "fix(googlechat): support spaceType field for DM vs Space detection",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Recognize current Google Chat DM payloads through `spaceType` and `singleUserBotDm`.\n- Prefer documented `spaceType` values over the deprecated legacy `type` field.\n- Cover direct and group classifications through the inbound monitor pipeline.\n\n## Scope\n\nThis fixes modern DM classification only. It does not change how `SPACE` or `GROUP_CHAT` messages pass group policy or create group sessions, so #58514 remains open.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/googlechat/src/monitor.test.ts`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local --stream-engine-output`\n",
